00:00:18.340 --> 00:00:20.610
director of community oral health,

00:00:20.610 --> 00:00:23.210
and director of the Pacific
Center for Special Care

00:00:23.210 --> 00:00:25.680
at the University of the Pacific

00:00:25.680 --> 00:00:28.653
Arthur Dugoni School of
Dentistry in San Francisco.

