on oral health for people
with disabilities and aging.

00:00:37.050 --> 00:00:38.860
And he's served on many national panels,

00:00:38.860 --> 00:00:40.720
including the IOM Committee on

00:00:40.720 --> 00:00:42.640
Oral Health Access to Services,

