00:41:33.840 --> 00:41:36.690
So, I think that the innovations
that I've talked about,

00:41:36.690 --> 00:41:38.230
I think there's a lot
of hope for the future,

00:41:38.230 --> 00:41:40.180
for being able to do things differently

00:41:40.180 --> 00:41:43.539
